d places.\r\n\r\n[SHOP NOW](https://bookshop.org/p/books/concrete-botany-the-ecology-of-plants-in-the-age-of-human-disturbance-joey-santore/d11d5ab94a9276d1?ean=9780760391884&next=t&utm_source=bs-ads&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=angquco2634489090&utm_term=email-promo-box&utm_content=B&utm_unitID=AUID44951)\r\nGET 20% OFF w/ code:\r\nEARTH26\t¬†\r\n[Llama Llama Graduation Day!](https://bookshop.org/lists/books-perfect-for-saying-con-grad-ulations?utm_source=bs-ads&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=angpepy2633736234&utm_term=email-promo-box&utm_content=B&utm_unitID=AUID44946)\r\nLlama Llama celebrates graduation day in this sweet and poignant installment of the New York Times bestselling Llama Llama series.\r\n\r\n[SHOP NOW](https://bookshop.org/lists/books-perfect-for-saying-con-grad-ulations?utm_source=bs-ads&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=angpepy2633736234&utm_term=email-promo-box&utm_content=B&utm_unitID=AUID44946)\r\nGET 15% OFF w/ code:\r\nPYR\r\n\r\n[Hoof Beats TPB](https://bookshop.org/p/books/hoof-beats-how-horses-shaped-human-history-william-t-taylor/5cd9e8f159dfd6e8?ean=9780520430808&next=t&utm_source=bs-ads&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=danunho2665788505&utm_term=email-promo-box&utm_content=B&utm_unitID=AUID44948)\r\nJourney to the ancient past with cutting-edge science and new data to discover how horses forever altered the course of human history.\r\n\r\n[SHOP NOW](https://bookshop.org/p/books/hoof-beats-how-horses-shaped-human-history-william-t-taylor/5cd9e8f159dfd6e8?ean=9780520430808&next=t&utm_source=bs-ads&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=danunho2665788505&utm_term=email-promo-box&utm_content=B&utm_unitID=AUID44948)\r\nGET 15% OFF w/ code:\r\nLOVEBOOKSELLERS\t¬†\r\n[Unstuck](https://bookshop.org/p/books/unstuck-a-writer-s-guide-ramona-ausubel/b07297ac6e54cde8?ean=9781963108712&next=t&utm_source=bs-ads&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=danzaun2694294024&utm_term=email-promo-box&utm_content=B&utm_unitID=AUID44957)\r\nFrom Ramona Ausubel comes the only writerвАЩs